1.  Copy the mpack.tar.gz to a  folder on ambari server host (like /tmp)
2.  Run the following command
    ambari-server install-mpack --mpack=/tmp/beacon-mpack-1.0-SNAPSHOT.tar.gz --verbose
3.  Restart Ambari server
    ambari-server restart
3.  Logon to ambari from a browser and click add service
4.  In the addservice wizard, you will see beacon as an available component
    Select it
5.  Install the service by following through the options

[root@hdp26 ~]# ambari-server install-mpack --mpack=/tmp/beacon-mpack-1.0-SNAPSHOT.tar.gz --verbose

